Package: vulnmind
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-click, python3-rich, python3-requests, python3-reportlab
Recommends: nmap
Description: Security scan analyzer for pentesters
 CLI tool that parses Nmap, Nikto, and Metasploit console output into
 structured findings. Matches CVEs against a built-in offline knowledge
 base, optionally enriches with live CVSS scores from NVD, and generates
 PDF / JSON / text reports with concrete remediation advice.
